0:36:44.780,0:36:50.600
uye kana richitonga mwoyo wangu, rinozotonga muromo wangu ne kukurudzira hunhu hwangu.

0:36:50.600,0:36:54.820
Nokuverenga Bhaibheri nekufungisisa kwenguva dzose, kuchatonga mwoyo wangu.

0:36:54.820,0:37:04.320
Uye rinofanirwa kuverengwa nekukanganwira, mweya wakasununguka.

0:37:04.320,0:37:11.140
Shoko rauri kuverenga unofanira kurishandisa mumunamato

0:37:11.140,0:37:14.940
Ndinokutenda, munin'ina. Mwari vakukomborere.

0:37:14.940,0:37:18.120
Ipai kuna mai vedu pano.

0:37:18.120,0:37:22.720
Maererano nedzidziso dzemu Porofita mangwanani ano, ndadzidza

0:37:22.720,0:37:31.640
kuti tinofanira kuverenga Bhaibheri redu zvishoma nezvishoma, kudzokorodza, uye nekunyatsoteerera.

0:37:31.640,0:37:36.620
Ndanga ndisiri kuita izvozvo; Ndaiverenga bhaibheri rangu chero pandaida.

0:37:36.620,0:37:39.760
Ndakanga ndisinganamate maererano ne Magwaro.

0:37:39.760,0:37:48.580
Ndaiverenga kubva musi weMuvhuro kusvika ku musi weChina uye kupedzisa Bhaibheri sekunge ndiri kuverenga bhuku.

0:37:48.580,0:37:57.300
Asi nhasi, ndadzidza kuti ndinofanira kuriverenga maererano ne zvinangwa zvitatu zvaatsanangura.

0:37:57.300,0:38:02.740
Ndinofanirwawo kuva nechido mubasa ra Mwari, icho chandisina nokuti ndiri muende weku chechi.

0:38:02.740,0:38:06.560
Ndinoenda kuchechi, ndogara pasi, ndodzokera kumba panongopera svondo.

0:38:06.560,0:38:09.800
Vauchirirei. Manzwa izvozvo here?

0:38:09.800,0:38:11.840
Vari kuti dzidzisa.

0:38:11.840,0:38:16.400
Ivo mupindi wechechi uye vaizodzokera kumba pakarepo mushure mekunge basa rechechi rapera,

0:38:16.400,0:38:20.520
achitenda kuti chegumi chake nemupiro wake (zvakakwana).

0:38:20.520,0:38:23.520
Rudzi hwai ...?

0:38:23.520,0:38:29.820
Kazhinji, vaizobvunza, "Avo vanoziva kuita zvimwe zvinhu muchechi, batanai nesu".

0:38:29.820,0:38:31.600
Asi ndaizongoenda muchinyararire.

0:38:31.600,0:38:34.100
Tiudzei zvimwe; tinoda kudzidza.

0:38:34.100,0:38:40.720
Saka, zvaita sokuti mu Porofita anga achitaura zvakanangana neni; Ndabatikana.

0:38:40.720,0:38:50.260
Ndinofanira kuzvitungamira ndega kwete kumirira vatungamiri vangu muchechi kuti vanditaurire zvandinofanira kuita.

0:38:50.260,0:38:53.480
Regai ndibatsire chero chikwata chandinokwanisa.

0:38:53.480,0:38:58.480
Batanai ne chikwata chinovandudza unhu hwenyu.

0:38:58.480,0:39:05.760
Usabatana nechikwata nekuda kwe chigaro chako kana chinzvimbo chako.

0:39:05.760,0:39:12.140
Joina chikwata chevanhu vausina chekuita navo kunze uko.

0:39:12.140,0:39:14.940
Iva nechimwe chinhu chekuita navo muchechi.

0:39:14.940,0:39:19.660
Vanhu vausina chekuita navo.

0:39:19.660,0:39:24.580
Tsvaga chikwata chavari ubatane navo

0:39:24.580,0:39:33.460
Vanhu vari pasi pako, chinzvimbo chako - joina chikwata ichocho muchechi kuti ushande machiri.

0:39:33.460,0:39:37.680
Hatifaniri kutakura sangano ratinaro kunze uko muchechi.

0:39:37.680,0:39:40.680
Izvi ndizvo zviri kukanganisa makereke nhasi.

0:39:40.680,0:39:51.520
Tinotora sangano ratinaro kunze toriunza muchechi.

0:39:51.520,0:39:56.780
Paunoona mapoka evanhu ari muchechi, akafanana ne masangano, ari kunze uko.

0:39:56.780,0:39:58.560
Izvozvo hazvitibatsire.

0:39:58.560,0:40:04.700
Kuti tibatsire hunhu hwedu, tinoda mumwe munhu watinogona kudzidza kubva kwaari -

0:40:04.700,0:40:11.280
mumwe munhu ane zvatisina, kwete munhu ane izvo tinazvo.

0:40:11.280,0:40:14.120
Iwe hauzove nechimwe chinhu chokudzidza kubva kwavari.

0:40:14.120,0:40:17.300
Iwe uri zvauri nokuda kwangu; ini ndiri zvandiri nekuda kwako.

0:40:17.300,0:40:27.840
Pausina simba, ini ndine simba; apo iwe une simba, ini ndine utera.

0:40:27.840,0:40:32.460
Mazvita

0:40:32.460,0:40:36.400
Ndinotenda Mwari nokuda kwemukana uyu.

0:40:36.400,0:40:48.160
Ndagara ndichinzwa kuti tinofanira kukanganwira vamwe, uye tisachengete zvigumbu patinenge tichinyengetera.

0:40:48.160,0:40:56.060
Asi nguva dzakawanda, ndinonyengetera ndakachengeta zvigumbu ne kusaregerera,

0:40:56.060,0:41:00.840
ndichivimba kuti Mwari anozondinzwira ngoni.

0:41:00.840,0:41:13.840
Asi ini ndinotenda Mwari nokuda kwe mukana uno kuti munhu wa Mwari akohomedza kukosha kwekunyengetera chete

0:41:13.840,0:41:17.480
kana mweya wako uri kubvumirana na Mwari.

0:41:17.480,0:41:19.200
Ndinokutendai, Munhu wa Mwari.

0:41:19.200,0:41:26.440
Uku kushanda mumba ma Mwari - saka kune nzvimbo yatinoda kuwedzera.

0:41:26.440,0:41:30.700
Pamunenge uchienda, unofanira kuenda ne vana vako pamwe chete.

0:41:30.700,0:41:32.320
Vanofanira kubatana nemi.

0:41:32.320,0:41:33.160
Ndinokutendai, changamire.

0:41:33.160,0:41:39.380
Ndinoyeuka, mumazuva iwayo - ndangariro dzamai vangu dzakaropafadzwa -

0:41:39.380,0:41:44.100
apo amai vangu vaienda kuchechi musi woMugovera ini ndakanga ndisingaendi kuchikoro,

0:41:44.100,0:41:50.420
vaizoona zvechokwadi kuti ndaidya zvokudya zve masikati muchechi

0:41:50.420,0:41:53.080
nokuti vaive nebasa rekuita muchechi.

0:41:53.080,0:41:58.280
Nokuda kwezvokudya, ndaifanira kutevera.

0:41:58.280,0:42:01.040
Vaizotakura zvokudya vobva vati, "Ugosangana neni".

0:42:01.040,0:42:07.020
Ndaiwanzotamba bhora asi ndaifanira kukanzura ndovatevera nokuti ndaifanira kudya.

0:42:07.020,0:42:12.460
Vechidiki vedu, chero zvavanoda, chero chii zvacho chatinofanira kuita kuti tivaunze pedyo -

0:42:12.460,0:42:16.740
Tinofanira kuita chinhu chimwe nechimwe chakakodzera kuti tivaswededze pedyo.

0:42:16.740,0:42:17.500
Ndinokutendai, changamire.

0:42:17.500,0:42:21.040
... kuvakwezva ne kuvauyisa kuna Mwari.

0:42:21.040,0:42:26.240
Kuitira kuti pavanenge vakura, vachanzwisisa zvawayiedza kuvaitira.

0:42:26.240,0:42:37.200
Asi pane rimwe zera, isu tinofanira kushandisa simba redu rehunhu kuti tivaswededze pedyo na Mwari.

0:42:37.200,0:42:37.940
Mazvita

0:42:37.940,0:42:45.640
Sekutaura kwandaita, onai kuti munobatana nevanhu vari pasi penyu;

0:42:45.640,0:42:49.000
dhipatimendi ravari ivo - batanai nedhipatimendi iroro.

0:42:49.000,0:42:55.320
Usaenda kuchechi kunobatana ne vari muchikwata chako kunze uko, zvavari kuita muchechi.

0:42:55.320,0:42:57.460
Ndinokutendai, madhamu. Mwari vakukomborerei.

0:42:57.460,0:43:02.140
Svondo Ye Musi We Svondo Pa SCOAN

0:43:02.140,0:43:12.920
Ndadzidza kuti minyengetero yangu inofanira kuzadzwa nezvandaidzidza muBhaibheri.

0:43:12.920,0:43:17.460
Kana ndikaverenga Bhaibheri nenzira iyoyo, chero nguva ipi yandinonamata,

0:43:17.460,0:43:22.280
Mweya Mutsvene aizonditungamirira kune chimwe chikamu cheBhaibheri.

0:43:22.280,0:43:29.100
nokuti Bhaibheri rine Rugwaro rwe zviitiko zvose zvehupenyu.

0:43:29.100,0:43:33.680
Uye isu hatigoni kuriverenga sekuverenga kwatinoita nhetembo dzedu.

0:43:33.680,0:43:41.180
Kana iwe ukariverenga mukutungamirirwa ne Mweya Mutsvene, chero nguva yaunonyengetera pamusoro penyaya,

0:43:41.180,0:43:48.260
Mweya Mutsvene achakutungamirira kune rumwe Rugwaro rwaunofanira kushandisa kugadzirisa nyaya yacho.

0:43:48.260,0:43:50.700
Ndizvo zvandadzidza.

0:43:50.700,0:43:55.100
Chechipiri, ndadzidza kuva nehanya nemabasa aMwari.

0:43:55.100,0:44:05.440
Punonyanya kuve ne ha'na nezvirongwa zva Mwari, Mwari anonyanya kuita han'a ne zvirongwa zvako.

0:44:05.440,0:44:16.600
Ndatenda. Pasi rose rinoda zvinhu zvakawanda asi izvo zvatinoda zviri muBhaibheri.

0:44:16.600,0:44:24.200
Sezvandanga ndichitaura - mumazuva iwayo, pandakanga ndiri muduku kwazvo, ndaiwanzotevera amai vangu.

0:44:24.220,0:44:28.320
Mai vangu vaiva mumwe wevanhu vaigara vachitsvaira ne kupukuta zvigaro zvechechi.

0:44:28.320,0:44:35.180
Chero nguva yavainge vachipukuta zvigaro ne kutsvaira, muromo wavo wainge uchitaura chinhu.

0:44:35.180,0:44:37.500
Handizivi zvavaitaura.

0:44:37.500,0:44:41.800
Ndakazoziva kuti vaizozevezera vachitaura

0:44:41.800,0:44:45.280
Rimwe zuva, ndakati, "Amai, murikuti chii? Munenge muchitaura pamunenge muchipukuta pukuta".

0:44:45.280,0:44:55.420
