0:44:55.420,0:45:00.420
Amai vangu vaizochenesa pasi ne zvigaro vachienda.

0:45:00.420,0:45:07.200
Dzimwe nguva mushure mokunge vataura taura, vaizotanga kuimba nziyo dze rumbidzo.

0:45:07.200,0:45:10.660
