0:45:10.660,0:45:13.920
hamundipinduri. Imi munoramba muchitaura mega. Hatizivi zvamuri kutaura ".

0:45:13.920,0:45:20.760
Vakati, "A, ndiri kuudza Mwari kuti, 'Pandiri kuchenesa imba Yenyu, chenesai upenyu hwangu ne ramangwana rangu,

0:45:20.760,0:45:23.040
basa rangu nevana vangu '".

0:45:23.040,0:45:29.600
Ndinofunga kuti ndiri mumwe wevanhu vavakapiwa na Mwari.

0:45:29.600,0:45:30.600
Ehe.

0:45:30.600,0:45:40.120
Akati, "Pandiri kuchenesa imba Yenyu, ndichitsvaira, chenesai mhuri yangu remangwana rangu, ne vana vangu".

0:45:40.120,0:45:49.240
Ndapota, farira zvirongwa zva Mwari.

0:45:49.240,0:45:51.040
Mazvita

0:45:51.040,0:45:55.540
Gungano re Kunze

0:45:55.540,0:45:58.080
Yave nguva yekunyengetera.

0:45:58.080,0:46:04.500
Iwe hauna nguva yekunamata, nepo munyengetero unofanira kunge uri nzira yemararamiro ako

0:46:04.500,0:46:08.360
Pose paunenge uri muchechi, chero chii chauri kuita panguva iyoyo,

0:46:08.360,0:46:11.720
ramba uchinyengetera.

0:46:11.720,0:46:25.580
Chinhu chipi zvacho chauya mumwoyo mako kuti uite, Mwari zvino achakurisa nzvimbo yako.

0:46:25.580,0:46:32.300
Iwe unozviwana iwe uchiva nezvakawanda mune zvauri kuita.

0:46:32.300,0:46:36.160
Ndinofunga kuti shoko ra nhasi ishoko rakazadzwa ne Mweya kwatiri tose muchechi.

0:46:36.160,0:46:37.020
Mazvita.

0:46:37.020,0:46:39.460
Ndine mhosva pa zvose.

0:46:39.460,0:46:42.500
Ndinoenda kuchechi ndichizvikudza,

0:46:42.500,0:46:46.900
uye ini ndinonzwa kuti kupa mari yangu yakasviba ndiyo zvose zviripo pakunamata Mwari.

0:46:46.900,0:46:49.920
Uchirirai mukoma wangu.

0:46:49.920,0:46:51.800
Wateerera kuna izvozvo here?

0:46:51.800,0:46:53.940
Urikuona here kuzvininipisa?

0:46:53.940,0:47:01.340
Ati, tinoenda kuchechi tichizvikudza, tinopa mari yedu yakasviba, uye tinoti tiri kutsigira kereke.

0:47:01.340,0:47:09.260
Kana uri kutsigira chechi yako nemari, chechi yacho yavepapi iye zvino?

0:47:09.260,0:47:13.580
Munhu wa Mwari, iyi imharidzo mufundisi wangu ange achitaura nezvayo nguva dzose.

0:47:13.580,0:47:18.880
Kuti tinofanira kuedza kuita chimwe chinhu mumba ya Mwari, chinoropafadza isu nemhuri dzedu.

0:47:18.880,0:47:23.920
Mharidzo iyi - dai kuri kuda kwangu - ndaida kuti iparidzwe muchechi yangu

0:47:23.920,0:47:26.880
kuitira kuti vanhu vazive zvazvinoreva kunamata Mwari.

0:47:26.880,0:47:28.500
Hatifaniri kuva vanhu vanongoenda kuchechi

0:47:28.500,0:47:31.300
Wateerera kuna izvozvo here?

0:47:31.300,0:47:37.640
Kana iwe ukaita chimwe chinhu mumba ma Mwari nemwoyo wako wose,

0:47:37.640,0:47:40.580
iwe uri kuzviitira kune zvizvarwa zvezera rako ne nemhuri yako.

0:47:40.580,0:47:43.380
Ndakuudzai pamusoro penyaya yamai vangu.

0:47:43.380,0:47:46.700
Mumazuva iwayo, pandakanga ndichiri muduku, ndaizotevera mai vangu.

0:47:46.700,0:47:50.620
Amai vakanga vachindimanikidza nechikafu.

0:47:50.620,0:47:55.360
Amai vaizozevezera (panguva yekuchenesa), uye gare gare vaizotanga kuimba.

0:47:55.360,0:47:57.320
Ndaizoti, "Amai!" Vaisazondipindura.

0:47:57.320,0:48:01.200
Ndaizovabvunza kuti, "Muri kutaura chii? Nguva ipi zvayo yamunenge muchipukuta ma bhenji,

0:48:01.200,0:48:04.940
muchitsvaira, imi munowanzoti chii? Imi munogara muchingo zevezera.

0:48:04.940,0:48:07.420
Ndinogara ndichiona muromo wenyu uchifamba famba ".

0:48:07.420,0:48:14.960
Vaizoti, "A, zvandiri kutaura, mwanangu - Mwari anofanira kuchenesa hupenyu hwangu, vana vangu.

0:48:14.960,0:48:17.280
'Ndiri kuchenesa imba yenyu, Ishe, chenesai ...' ".

0:48:17.280,0:48:20.800
Asi nhasi, ndinogona kuona zvechokwadi ...

0:48:20.800,0:48:25.740
Svondo Ye Musi We Svondo Pa SCOAN

0:48:25.740,0:48:30.820
Enda kuchechi unojoina avo vasiri vekirasi yako,

0:48:30.820,0:48:37.540
apo iwe unova mutorwa pakati pavo. Zviripo kukuninipisa.

0:48:37.540,0:48:39.300
Izvi ndizvo zvinoda Mwari.

0:48:39.300,0:48:41.000
Ndinokutendai, changamire, nokuda kwekudzidzisa kwenyu.

0:48:41.000,0:48:41.780
Ndinokutendai, Munhu wa Mwari.

0:48:41.780,0:48:43.700
Ndatenda. Wateerera kune mukoma wedu here?

0:48:43.700,0:48:45.900
Svondo Ye Musi We Svondo Pa SCOAN

0:48:45.900,0:48:48.540
Pane zvinhu zvakawanda zvaungaita.

0:48:48.540,0:48:50.660
Kune madhipatimendi akawanda okubatana nawo.

0:48:50.660,0:48:55.360
Kana tichiti tiri kutsigira kereke yedu, ndechipi chinzvimbo chechechi nhasi pasi rose?

0:48:55.360,0:48:59.640
Ini ndabatwa kwazvo nemharidzo yanhasi.

0:48:59.640,0:49:05.120
Ini ndiri munhu anochengeta zvigumbu.

0:49:05.120,0:49:10.540
Ndisati ndauya pano ndanga ndiine chigumbu

0:49:10.540,0:49:15.680
Nechigumbu chandinacho, dai ndisina kunzwa shoko renyu,

0:49:15.680,0:49:20.660
ne kuverenga bhaibheri rangu, ndingadai ndangopedza nguva yangu.

0:49:20.680,0:49:30.300
Ndisati ndauya pano, baba vangu vandikwataura ne mbama pasina chikonzero, saka chigumbu chiri mumwoyo mangu.

0:49:30.300,0:49:34.080
Nemhaka yezvamangoparidza, ndinofanira kurega chigumbu ichocho

0:49:34.080,0:49:38.360
ne kukudziridza tsika yekurega zvigumbu zvichipfuura,

0:49:38.360,0:49:42.660
kuitira kuti Mweya wa Mwari unogara nekusingaperi uuye kwandiri.

0:49:42.660,0:49:46.100
Kana ndikasaita izvozvo, Mweya wa Mwari haungauyi kwandiri.

0:49:46.100,0:49:52.820
Uye ini handigone kuverenga Bhaibheri zvishoma nezvishoma, kunyatsoteerera, nekudzokorora ...

0:49:52.820,0:49:56.060
... kana iwe uchinetseka.

0:49:56.060,0:49:57.080
Murovererei maoko

0:49:57.080,0:50:01.140
Saka ndiri kufara zvikuru nekugamuchira mharidzo iyi.

0:50:01.140,0:50:04.480
Ndinofanira kukanganwira baba vangu kuitira kuti ini ndifambire mberi.

0:50:04.480,0:50:07.540
Wateerera kuna izvozvo here?

0:50:07.540,0:50:11.540
Mati, munoda kuti vanhu vaite zvakanaka nguva dzose

0:50:11.540,0:50:17.520
uye iwe hauzivi kuti hupenyu huri paviri - zvakanaka ne zvakaipa

0:50:17.520,0:50:22.380
Iwe unofanira kunge uchitarisira zvakaipa, zvakanaka, zvakaipa, zvakanaka.

0:50:22.380,0:50:33.320
Iwe unoda zvinetso zvakawanda kuti zvikusimbise kuti utarise zvakakodzera nekunyatso cherechedza.

0:50:33.320,0:50:48.040
Iwe unoda mbama dzakawanda, kutambudzwa.

0:50:48.040,0:50:50.620
Iwe hausati wasvika.

0:50:50.620,0:50:54.240
Ino ndiyo nguva yaunofanira kunge uchitarisira kutambudzwa.

0:50:54.240,0:51:00.320
Vanhu vachakunyadzisa.

0:51:00.320,0:51:03.440
Izvozvo zvichakubatsira kuti uzvipire kumunyengetero.

0:51:03.440,0:51:06.920
Paunonyanya kunyadziswa, ndipo paunowedzera kuzvipira kumunyengetero.

0:51:06.920,0:51:14.620
Ndakakuudzai nguva yapfuura kuti matambudziko edu anotibatsira kuti tichengetedze kubatana kwedu na Mwari.

0:51:14.620,0:51:21.600
Ndiri kufara kunzwa kubva  kuna baba vangu pano, kuti vakakwaturwa zvisina kururama.

0:51:21.600,0:51:28.220
Ndinofunga kuti zvakanaka kwatiri, nokuda kwesimba redu.

0:51:28.220,0:51:34.480
Kunyanya nyanya kune avo vedu vari kuedza kusvika pane chimwe chigaro

0:51:34.480,0:51:38.880
ne avo vedu vanoshuvira kukura muna Mwari.

0:51:38.880,0:51:43.180
Tinofanira kutarisira izvi.

0:51:43.180,0:51:53.160
Tora nguva yako kuverenga nekudzidza hupenyu hwa T.B. Joshua - zvekare kangu.

0:51:53.180,0:51:56.500
Paunotarisa zvandakaita kare.

